high_descs: Turn around and take two steps then turn left and walk to the table.
Pick up the dirty wash cloth that's between two others on the table.
Turn around and go stand on the left side of the sink and look across the sink at the right side.
Wash the wash cloth in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Move a step to your right and walk back to where you got the dirty wash cloth from.
Put the wash cloth on the second shelf to the left of the white object please.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cloth on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to your right walk straight then turn left to the drawer
Pick up the dirty cloth on the drawer
Turn right and head to the left side of the sink
Put the cloth in the sink then rinse it
Turn right then head to the drawer
Put the cloth on the second level of the drawer beside the toilet paper
anns.task_desc: Put the clean cloth on the second layer of the drawer

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward then turn left and face the long greenish counter top
Pick up the dirty rag in the middle
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left , take a right at the toilet then turn right to face the side of the sink
Place the dirty rag into the sink and turn on the water to rinse it off. Then turn off the water and pick up the rag that is now clean.
Turn to the right and go to the long green counter that is ahead of you on the left
Place the clean rag on the second shelf to the left of the roll of toilet paper
anns.task_desc: Place a clean rag on a shelf
